<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n03074b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n03" href="#n03074b">N03 (VI.B.3)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n03all.htm#n03074b"> 74(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Power sent me a / bottle of ginger / cordial by a notorious drunkard / named Tommy Erp / also flowers &mdash; neither / reached me </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Arthur Power, Irish painter and art critic, was a friend of Joyce. Tommy Earp, a rich and eccentric Yorkshireman, was a member of Nancy Cunard&apos;s crowd. </mm> </dd></dl>
